title: Amiga Kickstart Roms 1.0 - 1.2 - 1.3 - 2.0 - 2.1 - 3.0 - 3.1
description:
An Amiga Kickstart Rom contains the code needed to boot standard Amiga hardware and many of the core components of AmigaOS. They are also required if you want to run games and apps in emulators such as WinUAE.
